text:
Social Conditions in Manhattan: The kitchen of a 4 room flat at No. 284 Mulberry Street and some of the apartments, 12 occupants (including 10 children). The rental for this space is .25. Note its clean appearance. Undoubtedly published by the New York Evening World on this date.

January 2, 1924.

Gift of New York World.
title: Social conditions in Manhattan.
